    <item>
      <title>波音公司表示，它仍在与司法部达成737多个Max崩溃的认罪协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/boeing-doj-say-still-working-on-plea-deal-over-737-max-crashes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司和美国检察官表示，他们仍在努力确定一项修订的协议，以解决针对两次致命的737 Max崩溃的刑事案件，这是在较早的计划被法官封锁三个月后，因为它包括与多样性，股权和包容性有关的规定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/boeing-doj-say-still-working-on-plea-deal-over-737-max-crashes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 19:11:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁斯蒂芬·费恩伯格（Stephen Feinberg）被确认为五角大楼副秘书</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/senate-backs-billionaire-feinberg-as-pentagon-deputy-secretary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议院确认亿万富翁斯蒂芬·费恩伯格（Stephen Feinberg）将在五角大楼担任第二任负责人，私募股权投资者承诺要解决长期存在的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/senate-backs-billionaire-feinberg-as-pentagon-deputy-secretary</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 18:22:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国，欧盟官员探索如何在特朗普的贸易战中前进</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/trump-tariffs-spur-eu-us-officials-to-find-way-forward-in-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟行政部门和美国官员的高级成员周五在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的金属关税引发了贸易战之后探索前进的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/trump-tariffs-spur-eu-us-officials-to-find-way-forward-in-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 18:09:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Gabbard宣布对美国情报界泄漏的调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/gabbard-announces-probe-into-us-intelligence-community-leaks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[她的办公室周五说，美国国家情报局局长塔尔西·加巴德（Tulsi Gabbard）对情报界使用的聊天室和信息共享平台进行了正式调查，并扩大了对聊天室和信息共享平台的调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/gabbard-announces-probe-into-us-intelligence-community-leaks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 18:04:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在G-7会议上，美国盟友的顶级外交官想知道卢比奥的立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/at-g-7-meeting-us-allies-top-diplomats-wonder-where-rubio-stands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在加拿大山区静修处，美国一些最亲密的盟友试图对私人对话和公众互动来神圣，而国务卿马可·卢比奥（Marco Rubio）确实站在他的老板上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/at-g-7-meeting-us-allies-top-diplomats-wonder-where-rubio-stands</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 17:49:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佩洛西（Pelosi）反对舒默（Schumer）的政府关闭撤退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/pelosi-comes-out-against-schumer-s-government-shutdown-retreat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南希·佩洛西（Nancy Pelosi）周五弯曲了她的政治肌肉，在参议院民主党领导人查克·舒默（Chuck Schumer）的威胁迫使共和党人迫使共和党人进行谈判或冒着美国政府关闭的风险后，对参议院民主党领导人查克·舒默（Chuck Schumer）进行了滑动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/pelosi-comes-out-against-schumer-s-government-shutdown-retreat</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 16:29:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加拿大总理卡尼说，美国贸易谈判取得了进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/carney-sworn-in-as-canada-leader-with-trade-dominating-agenda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）宣誓就职，担任加拿大24任总理，在与美国的爆炸性贸易战争中期，前中央银行家上台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/carney-sworn-in-as-canada-leader-with-trade-dominating-agenda</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 15:28:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对乌克兰停火乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/trump-asks-russia-to-spare-lives-of-surrounded-ukraine-troops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府表示，尽管弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）总统似乎拒绝立即停止暴力行为，但对乌克兰停火的可能性感到乐观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/trump-asks-russia-to-spare-lives-of-surrounded-ukraine-troops</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 13:44:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自由出版社说，哥伦比亚必须满足特朗普对资金的要求。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/trump-warns-columbia-it-must-meet-demands-to-regain-us-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据国土安全部的说法，联邦特工逮捕了一名巴勒斯坦学生，据称，特朗普政府扩大了驱逐人们“倡导暴力和恐怖主义”的努力，据称宣布签证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/trump-warns-columbia-it-must-meet-demands-to-regain-us-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 12:19:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列，美国解雇哈马斯提议释放美国人质</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/hamas-says-it-agreed-to-release-us-israeli-hostage-four-bodies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯说，它愿意释放所有美国以色列人质，包括仍然活着的人质，以以色列和美国都驳回了一个令人惊讶的举动，这是对结束战争的谈判努力无济于事的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/hamas-says-it-agreed-to-release-us-israeli-hostage-four-bodies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 11:26:39 GMT</pubDate>
